  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate that an intervention based on the motivational
      interview directed to patients with polypharmacy to improve the Therapeutic Adherence and to
      reduce the errors of Medication in major measure that the habitual intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
